Due to the recent interest in the newly elected President in the United States, Donald Trump and his extensive use of the platform Twitter, the topic selected for this study is Donald Trump. Through this study we will identify a set of Twitter accounts and tweets related this topic. From the set of users and tweets, we obtain the associated declared and dynamic networks. The centrality of the networks are investigated by computing some appropriate centrality metrics. For analysis and visualization we apply a tool called GEPHI. GEPHI is used to generate graphs for the given networks and obtain centrality metrics to analyze the structure of the networks and important nodes. The nodes in this context are twitter users.\
